<P>
JOHANNESBURG, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The listings of two South
African suspended companies, Anglovaal Insurance Holdings Limited
and Gold Fields Namibia Limited, were terminated at the close of
business Thursday, the Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE)
announced.
</P>
