alsof the Women's World Cup at Jack Kent Cooke Stadium.
</P>
<P>
"I think our whole team is strong enough to beat the U.S. team
maybe. If we give our best, there is no doubt," says defender
SteffiJones, daughter of a U.S. soldier who was stationed in
Germany.
</P>
