<HEADLINE> Australian Dollar Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, July 2 (Xinhua) -- The Australian dollar eased
marginally in quiet trading Friday in Sydney.
</P>
<P>
The Australian dollar ended at 66.74 U.S. cents from 66.86. At
the close, the Australian currency was buying 0.6511 euro from
0.6446 Thursday and 80.65 Japanese yen from 80.78. 
