<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Defense Minister Chi
Haotian, in a meeting today with his Namibian counterpart Erikki
Nghimtina, said that the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA) is
fully prepared to increase exchanges and cooperation with the
Namibian armed forces.
</P>
