<P>
NICOSIA, July 2 (Xinhua) -- The Cyprus stock market's average
daily volume rose to 14.6 million pounds (29.2 about million
dollars) this week from 8.8 million pounds (about 17.6 million
dollars) in the previous week.
</P>
<P>
