Fischer is scheduled to meet with Turkish President Suleyman
Demirel, Prime Minister Bulent Ecevit and Cem in Ankara on July 22.
</P>
<P>
The new German government led by Federal Chancellor Gerhard
Schroeder is expanding efforts to bring Turkey closer to the EU
and secure a candidacy status for it. 
