<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Nigerian Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, July 2 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news items in
leading Nigerian newspapers Friday.
</P>
<P>
New Nigerian:
</P>
<P>
-- Nigerian President Olusegun Obasanjo Thursday forwarded a
draft bill to the National Assembly, parliament of the west
African country, for the establishment of a Niger Delta
Development Commission.
</P>
<P>
The Post Express:
</P>
<P>
