-- Ten major group companies in the defense technology industry
were established yesterday in Beijing. They are based on the
former national corporations of the defense industry. The founding
of the group companies is an important step China has taken to
reform its management of the defense industry and accelerate its
modernization, according to Premier Zhu Rongji, who attended the
founding ceremony.
