<HEADLINE> U.S. Concerned over Bangladesh Buying MiG-29s </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The United States, which
refused to sell Bangladesh its F-16 warplanes several years ago,
was not happy about Dhaka's plan to buy eight Russian MiG-29s.
